Summers Says Averting Europe Breakdown ‘A Prudent Investment’

-- B y   J e n n i f e r   R y a n
-- 
2011-09-29T07:46:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/summers-says-averting-europe-breakdown-a-prudent-investment-.html
Former U.S. Treasury Secretary
 Lawrence Summers  said “avoiding the breakdown of the European
economy is I think a prudent investment.” He spoke in an
interview on BBC Radio 4 broadcast today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
